                  <provenance>
                     <p>While the circumstances under which this volume arrived in Britain remain
                        unclear, <persName role="fmo" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/97751058/"
                           key="person_97751058">Alexander Lindsay, 25th Earl of Crawford
                           (1812–1880)</persName> subsequently acquired it from an unidentified
                        source for his <orgName ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/295427552"
                           key="person_295427552">Bibliotheca Lindesiana</orgName> at Haigh Hall,
                           <placeName ref="http://vocab.getty.edu/page/tgn/7010384"
                           key="place_7010384">Wigan</placeName>.</p></provenance>
                  <provenance><p>Purchased by <persName role="dnr" key="person_f6379"
                           change="#prov-markup">Enriqueta Rylands (1843–1908)</persName> in <date
